    <p>: Did the Chinese-born pianist Lang Lang mean to send a pointed message with the song he played at the state dinner at the White House last Wednesday.</p>
    <p>(SOUNDBITE OF SONG, "MY MOTHERLAND")</p>
    <p>: Unidentified Woman: (Singing in foreign language)</p>
