    <p>BLOCK: What did she eat on Sunday?</p>
    <p>HILL: She ate frozen quail. Apparently, she has not been interested in any of the live bait that has been placed out. But when they put a frozen quail out, she apparently swooped down, grabbed the quail and made her escape back up to her perch.</p>
